data.description: NEAT AS A PIN! This beautifully remodeled three bedroom, two bath brick home inside Loop 304 in Crockett is a must see! This family home has wonderful curb appeal, is in a great neighborhood, and has many updates. From the moment you walk in the front door, you will love the family room attached to the kitchen with a breakfast nook. The primary bedroom has a private bath, while two guest bedrooms share a hall bath. This has home beautiful windows offering plenty of natural sunlight. Updates on this home include fresh paint inside and out, new 30-year architectural roof, and new countertops. This home is in a perfect location inside the Loop of Crockett, Texas. Don’t miss out on this wonderful opportunity to purchase this family home.
